          <a class="lightGreyText" title="Kindle Edition " href="/book/show/10323019-before-i-go-to-sleep">review of another edition</a>


        

          <div class="uitext greyText bookshelves">
            Shelves:
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/11057966-alex?shelf=favorites">favorites</a>, 
